snippet.textDisplay: This is such a beautiful and melodious song. And the fact that each and everyone in the video was genuinely enjoying the music is a testament to the beauty of the song. From Sona Mohapatra's little dance gigs in the middle to the ending "Bande Utkal Janani" by Rituraj, everything was beautiful. I don't understand either Odiya or Tamil, but I could feel the beats and the emotions behind the song.
snippet.textOriginal: This is such a beautiful and melodious song. And the fact that each and everyone in the video was genuinely enjoying the music is a testament to the beauty of the song. From Sona Mohapatra's little dance gigs in the middle to the ending "Bande Utkal Janani" by Rituraj, everything was beautiful. I don't understand either Odiya or Tamil, but I could feel the beats and the emotions behind the song.
